CS391 Mininet-based Lab #2: Link & Network Layer Forwarding

Author: Chaofan Lin, 50021911042, ACM Class @SJTU.

To run the mininet:
    $ python ./run_mininet.py [topo_file] -a

To run the POX:
    $ bash ./run_pox.sh

To run the switch:
    $ java -jar VirtualNetwork.jar -v [switch_name]

To run the router:
    $ java -jar VirtualNetwork.jar -v [router_name] -r [routing_table] -a [arp_cache]

File Structure:
    progAssign2/src/                (source code of the implementation)
    README              (this file)
    Mininet-Lab2-V3.docx   (assignment doc)
